              <td class="events">
                <h3><a class="anchor" id="top" name="soulconcert"></a>Soul Symphony Concert, Saturday 7th December</h3>
                <p>Join Soul Symphony Choir and special guests for an uplifting musical evening, 7 December 2019.</p>
                <p>After a spectacular Summer Concert, Soul Symphony are excited and eager to inspire, encourage and entertain their much loved audience. The show will feature gospel, pop and other festive classics with instrumentals, singing and spoken word. You won’t want to miss this night of soulful harmonies and festive cheer!</p>
                <p>Proceeds from the concert will be donated to charity</p>
                <p>6.30PM at Christ Church Purley, Brighton Road (between 861 and 863), Purley CR8 2BN</p>
                <p><%= link_to "Tickets are available from www.ticketsource.co.uk/booking/t-rdkdgr", "https://www.ticketsource.co.uk/booking/t-rdkdgr" %></p>
              </td>
              <td class="events"><%= link_to image_tag("small-images/Soul symphony100.jpg", alt: "Soul Symphony"), "http://www.soulsymphony.co.uk" %>
              </td>
