                <p>Come and join us at St Antony's, Wentworth Way, CR2 9EW, for Carols with Soul Symphony choir. 5.30 pm on Sunday 8 December. <%= link_to "See our flyer", "resource/StAntony_carols.pdf" %>.</p>
